{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"胜利红旗飘飘举——祝古巴革命胜利四周年","authors":["臧克家"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":12,"day":29}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利红旗飘飘举"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——祝古巴革命胜利四周年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"臧克家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古人道：惺惺惜惺惺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日是：英雄爱英雄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们步枪加小米，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创造了革命光荣史；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们凭七支步枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给墨黑的美洲开天窗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时代不一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经验却相同："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管你反动派连环套像长城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有一步跨过去的雄风；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕什么铜墙铁壁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢拳头给你打上个大窟窿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直着腰，挺着胸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严寒里迎着大北风！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头顶天，脚立地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"威胁不怕欺骗不理！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是吃了熊心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是吞了豹胆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀中有个宝中宝："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马克思主义当先！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十三个兄弟世界上立，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是后来的；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后来者，好伴侣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命健儿不怕虎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利红旗飘飘举，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拂去乌云现青天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间不长才四年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奴隶国土成花园。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们正忙着迎新年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们的纪念在眼前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提起笔来写双喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利双喜贴天边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我眼前有一颗星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它亮在美洲上空；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我心里有个古巴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天黑夜光荧荧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我手里有一杯酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起杯子祝朋友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我口里有一首歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱战斗的友谊万古千秋！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}